---
title: Corn & Carrot Fritters with Cheddar, Roasted Potatoes & Herby Mayo
description: There's no better way to get your veggies than by adding them to cheesy golden fritters, gently pan-fried for a gorgeous finish. With an
extra dose of goodness from the robust side salad and a drizzle of delicious herby mayo, this is a colourful garden medley that you'll love!

